{
  "stem": "9503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like a central focus point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You couldn't escape it, because no matter where you went there it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It really went through the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We ended up getting a room just for my father, and my mother, and myself, which was a privilege.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't remember how long we lived in that room, probably maybe four or five months.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In early September, there was a dictum-- oh, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I want to tell you about my doll.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father was put in charge of making the purchases of electrical equipment that was needed for the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they sent him to Amsterdam to get whatever the necessary stuff was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother and I stayed so they knew he'd come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And somehow or other, he got a hold of my doll, and he brought it back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember, you know, this doll coming back to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't even ask where did you go to get it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It just was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this doll was a very-- this doll stands for an awful lot of, I think, where my emotions went.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I don't remember otherwise being overly upset or even crying a lot, in fact, probably none at all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before going to the camp being very unhappy and even sometimes crying myself to sleep but during the camp, none of that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Early September, there was a dictum that everybody with children had to leave Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944, September.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because my parents had me, we went and transport September 4 supposedly to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
